<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Loopy Fries - Tornado Fries</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Tornado Fries</h1>
    <p>Home of the Original <strong>Loopy Fries</strong></p>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <h2>Try Our Crispy & Flavorful Loopy Fries</h2>
    <p>Deliciously twisted. Available in Small and Large sizes.</p>
    <a href="#order" class="btn">Order Now</a>
  </section>

  <section class="features">
    <h2>Why You'll Love Loopy Fries</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>üî• Super crispy</li>
      <li>üçü Packed with flavor</li>
      <li>üí∏ Affordable and satisfying</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="pricing">
      <p><strong>Small:</strong> Rs. 320</p>
      <p><strong>Large:</strong> Rs. 390</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="order-form" id="order">
    <h2>Place Your Order</h2>
    <form>
      <label for="name">Your Name:</label>
      <input type="text" id="name" required>

      <label for="size">Choose Size:</label>
      <select id="size" required>
        <option value="">--Select--</option>
        <option value="small">Small - Rs. 320</option>
        <option value="large">Large - Rs. 390</option>
      </select>

      <label for="address">Delivery Address:</label>
      <textarea id="address" rows="3" required></textarea>

      <button type="submit">Confirm Order</button>
    </form>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>¬© 2025 Tornado Fries. All Rights Reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
